      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle has been preserved with uncompromising attention to detail, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in a state of absolute preservation. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance and reliability that mirror its original factory specifications. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of such caliber, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new.",
