    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it still feels and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken obsessive care of it\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43900.0,
