      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a museum-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of high-revving naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system for optimal cam timing. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a professional rear subframe reinforcement and conrod bearing replacement using OE-spec components. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp-shifting manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery and exceptional turn-in characteristics. The exterior finish remains in concours condition, while the interior maintains its original tactile integrity. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a mechanically sorted, structurally sound icon of the M division\u2019s golden era.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Single owner. No accidents. Full service history. Clean title.",
      "price": 42500.0,
